                        Who is this course for
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
                        This course is for you if you have no previous experience and want to get your first care job, or if you
                        are already working in care and want recognition for your current skills. If you&#39;re already working in
                        care and work mainly under supervision this course will help you to increase your skills and take on
                        more responsibility. To be successful in this field you must have an interest in caring for and helping
                        people, be kind, reliable, empathetic and compassionate towards the people you support.
                    </dd>
                    <dd class="govuk-summary-list__actions">
