                    <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
                        Four GCSE grades 3-1 (D-G) including 3 (D) in English language, or a merit in Level 1 Diploma.
                        You will need a clear DBS enhanced disclosure in order to start the course.
                    </dd>
                    <dd class="govuk-summary-list__actions">
                        <a class="govuk-link" href="#">
